prodNameC: 羅氏可霸斯免疫分析人類絨毛膜促素性腺激素STAT檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Reagents - working solutions
M     Streptavidin-coated microparticles (transparent cap), 1 bottle, 6.5 mL:
       Streptavidin-coated microparticles 0.72 mg/mL; preservative.
R1    Anti-hCG-Ab~biotin (gray cap), 1 bottle, 9 mL: Biotinylated monoclonal anti-hCG antibody (mouse) 2.3 mg/L; phosphate buffer 40 mmol/L, pH 7.5; preservative.
R2    Anti-hCG-Ab~Ru(bpy) (black cap), 1 bottle, 10 mL: Monoclonal anti-hCG antibody (mouse) labeled with ruthenium complex 6.0 mg/L; phosphate buffer 40 mmol/L, pH 6.5; preservative.

CalSet - working solutions
• HCG STAT Cal1: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 1
• HCG STAT Cal2: 2 bottles, each for 1.0 mL of calibrator 2
Human chorionic gonadotropin (from urine) in two concentration ranges (approx. 10 mIU/mL and approx. 5000 mIU/mL) in a buffered human serum matrix.
applicantName: 台灣羅氏醫療診斷設備股份有限公司

efficacy: 利用免疫分析法於體外定量檢測人類血清及血漿中人類絨毛膜促性腺激素。
